snippet.title: Nintendo Switch The Binding of Isaac: Afterbirth+ Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Developed and published by Nicalis, Inc., The Binding of Isaac: Afterbirth+ will release on Nintendo Switch in Spring 2017 at retail and digitally via the Nintendo eShop.
